```

---

## **6. DoS (Denial of Service) zaifliklarini topish**  

### **ðŸ“Œ FTP serverga DoS hujum imkoniyatini tekshirish**  
```bash
nmap --script=ftp-proftpd-backdoor -p 21 192.168.1.1
```
âœ” **Misol:** **SIP VoIP serverga DoS hujumlarini aniqlash**  
