```

---

## **7. Oâ€˜chirilgan yoki yashirin xizmatlarni topish**  

### **ðŸ“Œ Yashirin SSH yoki Telnet xizmatlarini aniqlash**  
```bash
nmap --script=ssh-hostkey,telnet-encryption -p 22,23 192.168.1.1
```

âœ” **Misol:** **Yashirin veb-serverlar yoki admin panellarni topish**  
